To compile in XDAQ environment make sure that the environment 
variables XDAQ_ROOT and BUILD_HOME are correctly set. Then type 

make 
make install

The include files and libraries will be installed under the tree
in BUILD_HOME. 

To generate RPMs (binary and dev) type

make rpm
make installrpm

To install independent from a XDAQ tree make sure that the 
environment variable XDAQ_ROOT is NOT set and type 

make

Further information/documentation in the API docu and in the 
manual available under:
./doc/index.html

